00:00:39.682 --> 00:00:41.140
about the kind of
Indian developers

00:00:41.140 --> 00:00:42.990
you have worked with,
the kind of partners,

00:00:42.990 --> 00:00:46.640
and what do you see is a common
trend emerging out of India.

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:48.500
